+            "read to the last N tokens (+ --verify-sink first S), reusing the split-KV tree-verify "
+            "kernel. The verify prefix attention is mask-free (skip_prefix_custom_mask), so windowing "
+            "is clean (suffix tree-mask geometry derives from the windowed kv_indptr). Cuts the O(ctx) "
+            "verify read that collapses split-KV verify at depth. -1 (default) = off. LOSSY spec "
+            "(reduced-KV verify changes accept/reject) — quality-gate at depth before use.",
